data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!  LOOKING FOR A GREAT DEAL... HERE IT IS !  Beautiful 4 bedrooms and 3 bath home with a Pool/Spa and a large RV parking.    This great home is situated North of the Freeway in one of the most desired communities in Moreno Valley. Great floor with a formal living and dining room, a large family room, two cozy fireplaces one in the family room and another in the large master bedroom with a balcony. Nice kitchen with breakfast area.   Inside laundry room.   NEW AIR CONDITIONING, WATER HEATER and STOVE (Less than a year old).    The backyard is also perfect for gatherings with a gorgeous pool, concrete throughout and space for the RV on the side of the house and still room for all your toys. Within walking distance from an Elementary and Junior school, shopping and the 60 Freeway.  Just need some TCL and updates.   LOW TAXES AND NO HOA!!  Hurry it won't last at this price !
